<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>verification</title>
</head>

<body style="padding: 3vh 5vw; background-color: #ededed;">
  <div style="padding: 1vh 3vw; background-color: white; border-radius: 10px;">
    <h2>
      Action Required: Verify Email
    </h2>

    <p>
      You are receiving this email because
      <b>
        <%= email %>
      </b>
      has not been verified. <br>
      Please, enter the following code for verification:
    </p>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;">
      <%= verificationCode %>
    </h3>

    <ul>
      <li>If you have any problems, please use the
        <b>
          <%= APP_NAME %>
        </b>
        website to contact us.
      </li>
      <li>If you do not confirm this request, no further action is required.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Best, <br>
      the <%= APP_NAME %> team</p>
  </div>

  <p style="padding: 1vh 3vw; color: grey;">This email tells you about important changes to your account.</p>
</body>

</html>